text: Strehaia is a town in Mehedinţi County, Oltenia, Romania. Around 10,506 people lived in Strehaia in 2011.VOLUMUL I: POPULAŢIA STABILĂ (REZIDENTĂ) – STRUCTURA DEMOGRAFICĂ. www.recensamantromania.ro. Retrieved December 31, 2021. (Romanian) ==References== Strehaia Category:Mehedinți County
